Invite colleagues, coworkers, family members and friends to a special retirement celebration with elegant custom photo party invitations. The picture and all wording on this template are simple to personalize. (IMAGE PLACEMENT TIP: An easy way to position a photo exactly how you want is to crop it before uploading to the Zazzle website.) The modern burgundy and gold design features one photo of the retiree, a maroon red ombre background, stylish script calligraphy, and classic vintage art deco typography. Please note that gold is printed color, not metallic foil. The gender neutral design is also suitable for either a man or a woman. Cheers, Congratulations and Happy Retirement! Price:$2.06
